# Exclude categorical data from column 1 and Run PCA
body_sample <- body[, -1]
# Run PCA
body_pca <- prcomp(body_sample, scale= TRUE)
#Summary of analysis

fviz_pca_biplot(body_pca, label="var", habillage = body$Gender)

fviz_pca_biplot(body_pca, label = "var", habillage = body$Gender) + 
  scale_color_manual(values = c("Male" = "orange", "Female" = "purple"))
